import React from 'react';
import { Container, Box, Typography, List, ListItem } from '@mui/material';

const Experience = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg">
      <Box
        style={{
          minHeight: '100vh',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          justifyContent: 'flex-start',
          alignItems: 'flex-start',
          textAlign: 'left',
          padding: '5% 0',
          marginTop: '64px'
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h6">Unstructured, San Francisco, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Developer Advocate Engineer/Sales Engineer (Jul 2023 - Dec 2023)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Developed tailored Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) systems for clients leveraging GPT4-Turbo or OSS.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Fine-tuned open-source embedding models and LLMs, including LLama 2, for on-premise systems.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Implemented LLM solutions on AWS Bedrock and Sagemaker for customers.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Authored external technical documents, blogs, and social media posts to maximize product usage.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Led teamâ€™s community outreach program, scaling API adoption from 0 to 3500 users.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Built and maintained comprehensive technical documentation for OSS and hosted solutions.</ListItem>
        </List>
        {/* Gemini / Nifty Gateway */}
        <Typography variant="h6">Gemini / Nifty Gateway, San Francisco, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Data Scientist (Jan 2022 - Jul 2023)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Developed data dashboards leveraging Looker to track product performance and user engagement.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Served as a key liaison between clients and engineering and product management teams.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Spearheaded operations for a team of ten, generating over $4M in revenue in the past year.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Contributed significantly to a team effort that expanded the user base of a self-service tool from zero to 1,500 users.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Managed company go-to-market strategy for global expansion, increasing product revenue by 30%.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Wrote technical and non-technical documentation for clients.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Generated external financial reports leveraging Snowflake and Pandas.</ListItem>
        </List>

        {/* Intertek */}
        <Typography variant="h6">Intertek, Menlo Park, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Systems Engineer (June 2021 - Jan 2022)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Conducted data center risk assessments on Google cloud infrastructure.</ListItem>
        </List>

        {/* University of California, Davis */}
        <Typography variant="h6">University of California, Davis, Davis, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Deep Learning Researcher (May 2019 - June 2020)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Led a research team that leveraged open-source, SOTA computer vision models, such as CNNs, on drone-captured imagery.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Collected large quantities of raw drone data and managed the ML pipeline including preprocessing, training, and testing of multiple CNNs.</ListItem>
        </List>

        {/* PlateIQ */}
        <Typography variant="h6">PlateIQ, Emeryville, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">Software Engineer (June 2018 - Sep 2018)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Developed computer vision models for invoice layout type detection, and field localization achieving 91% accuracy.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Managed and processed roughly labeled data from Mechanical Turk.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Developed NLP error correction models, improving OCR system accuracy by 10%.</ListItem>
        </List>

        {/* TextRecruit */}
        <Typography variant="h6">TextRecruit, San Jose, CA</Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">AI Engineer (Aug 2017 - Sep 2018)</Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>Developed chatbots for Human Resources using IBM Watson.</ListItem>
          <ListItem>Created and maintained a robust automated testing suite for software stability and reliability.</ListItem>
        </List>

        {/* Additional experiences can be formatted similarly */}
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Experience;
